Description: Replay Guitar Exchange is proud to present this Jackson Dinky Reverse electric guitar from the year 1997, with a killer blue flame top and a stylistic reverse headstock. The alder solidbody sports the bolt-on maple neck and rosewood fingerboard, offering smooth comfort and readily easy playability. A Jackson branded floyd rose keeps your axe in tune while executing roaring dive bombs, accentuated by two Duncan Designed humbucker pickups that give an aggressive and heavy tone. This model is in Very Good condition, with minor dings and scratches about the body, and an estimated 90% of fret life remaining. This Jackson Dinky Reverse is sure to storm the stage with the fury of a metal shredder, available now at Replay Guitar Exchange! As always, feel free to contact our store for more details, or with any questions. Weight: 7 lbs. 6 oz.
